text: Guy Marchand (23 June 1943 - 22 June 2015) was a French wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2015 deaths Category:French male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of France Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dijon
